From: rcg1597@zeus.tamu.edu (GUYNN, RICHARD CARL)
Subject: Re: MGBs and the real world
Article-I.D.: zeus.5APR199321160020
Distribution: world
Organization: Texas A&M University, Academic Computing Services
Lines: 34
